{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_011cDnjUqyTgwUvPbrHDL3dc","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_013jb3PH5dEfo5YxT3y6iQKX","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/Users/luizantonio/Documents/Antigravity/AxenWP/fix_plan.md","old_string":"### 7. Shared httpx client for GHL/Z-API services\n- **Problem:** New `httpx.AsyncClient` created per-request in ghl_service and zapi_service\n- **Impact:** Connection overhead, no HTTP/2 multiplexing or keep-alive benefits\n- **Fix:** Use a module-level or app-level shared client with proper lifecycle","new_string":"### 7. [DONE] Shared httpx client for GHL/Z-API services\n- **Problem:** New `httpx.AsyncClient` created per-request in ghl_service and zapi_service\n- **Impact:** Connection overhead, no HTTP/2 multiplexing or keep-alive benefits\n- **Fix:** Use a module-level or app-level shared client with proper lifecycle"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3361,"cache_read_input_tokens":36437,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":3361},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c65344f3-6aa1-4b02-b3ae-01430f0d6aae","uuid":"0d5aaa8e-bc4f-4a21-bf82-c26e355c17ed"}
